explanations.reason: The paper focuses on sociodemographic factors associated with non-disclosure of HIV sero-status to sexual partners in Maputo, Mozambique. It uses statistical methods like univariate and multivariable logistic regression models to analyze these factors. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, neural networks, or related methodologies in the title or abstract. The study is purely epidemiological and does not involve any computational or machine learning approaches.
